{{zh-forms|[[请]][[神]][[容易]][[送]][[神]][[难]]|[[請神容易送神難]]}}
=={{cmn}}==
===Etymology===
Literally: It's easy to invite a god, but not so easy to get rid of a god.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=qĭng shén róngyì sòng shén nán|pint=qing3shen2rong2yi4song4shen2nan2|tra=請神容易送神難|sim=请神容易送神难|rs=讠08}}
# Some people are only too willing to help you, but then you can't get rid of them.
